      • uiReadyGroup

        public static GroupBuilder uiReadyGroup()
        Builder for a UI ready group. The group will have the following fields set:
        • Name - auto generated, of the form GroupN
        • Group type - "general"
        • Parent - the root group
        • Supervisor - su, the unrestricted user
        • Security zone - the default security zone
        Returns:
        a new builder
